            <title>[CASSANDRA-4640] Make CQL3 the default</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4640</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In 1.2, CQL3 will be final and thus I believe we should make it the default for CQL (and thus cqlsh).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Of course CQL2 will still be available, one will just have to call set_cql_version (for thrift) or &apos;cqlsh -2&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
